[SN]TITLE[SN]
Turf Lodge shooting: Man shot in legs in west Belfast attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been shot in both legs in a paramilitary-style attack in west Belfast.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The shooting, which was reported to police shortly before 21:00 BST on Saturday, happened at Ardmonagh Gardens in the Turf Lodge estate.
The victim was taken to hospital for injuries which are not believed to be life-threatening.
Police have appealed for anyone with any information about the attack to contact them.
